<h2 class="bold font-l">The Blue Duck gets murdered.</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The Blue Duck, a piece of art that Dilbert created, generates backlash when the Pointy-Haired Boss shows off the Blue Duck on his body on the Jumbotron with a heaping of Fan Disservice. </p>
</div>
